ed="T" n="0776a01"/><persName key="A004596">釋圓智</persName>，俗姓<name>張</name><ptr target="#n1566"/>，<placeName key="PL000000018931"><placeName>豫章</placeName><placeName>海昏</placeName></placeName>人也。總丱之年，頓<lb
ed="T" n="0776a02"/>求出離，<anchor xml:id="beg0776sgsz1"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0776sgsz1"/><persName key="A003974">涅槃和尚</persName>，躬執<anchor xml:id="beg0776sgsz2"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>鉼</sic><corr>缾</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0776sgsz2"/>屨。爰登戒地，<lb
ed="T" n="0776a03"/>誓叩禪門，見乎<persName key="A010510">藥山</persName>，示其心決。後居<placeName key="PL000000028631"><placeName>長沙</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0776a04"/><placeName>道吾山</placeName></placeName>，海眾相從，猶蜂蟻之附王焉。以<date key="j20263202026320" when-iso="+0835-10-10"><name><anchor xml:id="beg0776sgsz3"/>太<anchor xml:id="end0776sgsz3"/><lb
ed="T" n="0776a05"/>和</name>九年乙卯九月十一日</date>長逝，享年六十七。<lb
ed="T" n="0776a06"/>闍維，得不灰之骨數片，<anchor xml:id="beg0776sgsz4"/>腦<anchor xml:id="end0776sgsz4"/>蓋一節，特異而清<lb
ed="T" n="0776a07"/>瑩，其色如金，其響如銅。乃建塔于<placeName key="PL000000028722">石霜山</placeName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0776a08"/>勅謚<persName key="A004596">脩一大師</persName><placeName key="PL000000057012">寶相之塔</placeName>。得其道者則<persName key="A010581">普會</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0776a09"/>焉。<persName key="A004596">智<roleName>公</roleName></persName>初領悟<persName key="A010510">藥山</persName>宗旨，<persName key="A010510">儼<roleName>師</roleName></persName>誨之曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A010510">吾</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0776a10"/>無寶玉大弓以為分器，今賞<ref type="person" target="#A004596">汝</ref>犢鼻一腰，<lb
ed="T" n="0776a11"/>雖云微末，而表親褻歟？」<placeName key="PL000000028928">南嶽</placeName>僧<persName key="A010511">玄泰</persName>著<lb
ed="T" n="0776a12"/>碑頌。</p>
